# Commit Authorship

Do not add Cursor as a co-author in any commit message for this repository.

Never include these trailers or identities:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `cursoragent`
- `cursoragent@cursor.com`

Commit messages should only include human authorship explicitly requested by the
user.
